2. If the released software contains graphical user interface, a text or image logo of (Powered by ParaEngine) is required to show in a user visible place during software startup. The notice can only be removed if any of the above copyrighted parties agrees via contract. 
3. If any logo appears in user generated works(worlds or video streams) made with modifed version of Paracraft, the Paracraft Logo should be shown as well.
4. Commercial use of paracraft or its modified versions should pay 5% of total revenue only if its revenue exceed 10000 USD or equivalent amount in other currency. Contact the author for additional permission to remove 5% of total revenue requirement.

